Ralph Fiennes, Jodie Comer, Aaron Taylor-Johnson, Alfie Williams, director Danny Boyle, and writer/producer Alex Garland sit down with RT correspondent Mark Ellis to talk about their upcoming movie ’28 Years Later’.
